OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain moves
OL,6,Fsoutheast from the west and northwest,
OL,7,Fwith brief heavy showers in western
OL,8,FScotland. Eastern and southeastern
OL,9,Fareas stay mostly dry. Late clear
OL,10,Fspells in the far west and northwest
OL,11,Fmay allow temperatures to dip,
OL,12,Felsewhere remains mild overall.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FA bright start in the east,
OL,15,Fotherwise generally rather cloudy with
OL,16,Foutbreaks of rain. The rain turning
OL,17,Fheavier and more persistent later in
OL,18,Fthe west. Brisk winds but staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
